<section id="bounce">
  <h2>data-effect="bounce"</h2>
  <p>Continuous vertical bounce animation. The element bounces up and down in a rhythmic loop. The <span class="element-badge" data-type="pack">kawaii</span> pack overrides this with a spring-loaded hover-only variant when loaded.</p>

